            <span>Steve McConnell</span>
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="sec-4">
    <div class="section-content">
        <div class="section-decoration-x x-2 white right wow anim-del-3"></div>
        <h1 class="wow animate__animated animate__fadeInLeft">Skills</h1>
        <div class="section-line"></div>
        <div class="row align-items-center justify-content-around">
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                <div class="wow animate__animated animate__fadeInUp anim-del-0">
                    <div class="skills-heading">
                        <h2><i class="fab fa-shopware"></i></h2>
                        <h3>Shopware 6</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p>As a Shopware 6 Certified Template Designer I deal with the<br>development of new and modern stores on a daily basis.</p>
                    <a href="https://www.shopware.com" target="_blank">
                        <button class="btn btn-primary">Get in touch</button>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                <div class="wow animate__animated animate__fadeInUp anim-del-1">
                    <div class="skills-heading">
                        <h2><i class="fab fa-vuejs"></i></h2>
                        <h3>VueJS</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p>Working with VueJS in web development is completely<br>normal nowadays. Therefore I deal with this framework.</p>
                    <a href="https://vuejs.org" target="_blank">
                        <button class="btn btn-primary">Get in touch</button>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                <div class="wow animate__animated animate__fadeInUp anim-del-2">
                    <div class="skills-heading">
                        <h2><i class="fab fa-node"></i></h2>
                        <h3>NodeJS</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p>NodeJS is known for its flexibility and reliability.<br>Fun Fact, this page is written in NodeJS</p>
                    <a href="https://nodejs.org" target="_blank">
